DTSTAMP:20251215T055026Z
DTSTART:20251220T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join a restoration work party at East Duwamish GS: S Chicago St
	. \\nHelp take care of the forest along this neighborhood trail! Depending
	 on the time of the year\\\, we’ll be pulling and removing ivy\\\, cutting
	 back and digging out blackberry or planting new plants\; but always havin
	g a good time! \\nThe forest is in South Beacon Hill/Rainier Beach. Use 86
	31 39th Ave S as an approximate address for the upper trail entrance\\\, w
	here volunteers will meet.  \\nOpen to the public\\nAll ages OK \\nLearn m
	ore + register here\n\nFrom The Seattle Parks Foundation
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/east-duwamish-work-party-2
	4/
