DTSTAMP:20251215T055026Z
DTSTART:20251220T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join a restoration work party at Jackson Park Golf Course. \\nH
	elp restore native plants along this lovely trail around the public golf c
	ourse. We’re out there every third Saturday. Enjoy the birds\\\, trees\\\,
	 Thornton Creek\\\, and views into the golf course (and the occasional gol
	f ball find!) \\nLearn more + register\n\nFrom The Seattle Parks Foundatio
	n
