BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:VrrPtnsDQVNSYykaSjulB
SUMMARY:Capehart Forest with Friends of Discovery Park
DTSTAMP:20251215T055026Z
DTSTART:20251221T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Discovery Park. \\nCape
	hart Forest is the most wildlife-diverse area in Discovery Park. Come help
	 us promote forest health and increase its biodiversity by weeding out inv
	asives\\\, mulching and aerate the soil to encourage symbiotic fungi\\\, a
	nd plant this years native shrubs and groundcovers. \\nRegister\n\nFrom Th
	e Seattle Parks Foundation
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/capehart-forest-with-frien
	ds-of-discovery-park/
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
