BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:lkYkrgEHyAP1lbqHGcNwq
SUMMARY:English Ivy Removal - Forest Fun for Everyone
DTSTAMP:20251215T055026Z
DTSTART:20251227T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Kubota Gardens Natural 
	Area. \\nSo much ivy! Every month\\\, volunteers make a big difference by 
	removing ivy so that trees\\\, bushes\\\, ferns and other native plants ha
	ve room to grow. As you will quickly see\\\, the ivy covers large areas of
	 ground and is climbing up trees. We also are discovering small Himalayan 
	blackberry plants and getting those out immediately is a priority. No expe
	rience is needed – just bring your energy and interest in making a differe
	nce! \\nLearn more + register\n\nFrom The Seattle Parks Foundation
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/english-ivy-removal-forest
	-fun-for-everyone-6/
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
