BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:2vTCVdmGDcdEuvedw2Qt3
SUMMARY:Brandon Street Natural Area Restoration
DTSTAMP:20251215T055026Z
DTSTART:20260113T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Longfellow Creek GS: Br
	andon Street. \\nJoin the DNDA Nature program and help restore important h
	abitat in the critical Longfellow Creek Watershed. \\nEach work party begi
	ns with a short informal forest ecology discussion and we spend the remain
	der of the time performing various restoration activities\\\, including pl
	anting native trees and shrubs\\\, removing invasive species\\\, mulching 
	previously-planted areas and more. We work rain or shine! \\nRegister\n\nF
	rom The Seattle Parks Foundation
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/brandon-street-natural-are
	a-restoration-2/
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
