UID:flPrOpkU4B9Q6wVX4LUIo
SUMMARY:MUCC Work Party March 8th
DTSTAMP:20251215T055026Z
DTSTART:20260308T090000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Magnolia Park. \\nThere
	 is work to be done to reclaim Magnolia Park S.E. Forest in Magnolia Park.
	 Non-native plants have taken over\\\, and volunteers are needed to help d
	efend this beautiful natural area. Join neighbors and friends to help out 
	and learn about how we plan on bringing this forest back to a natural envi
	ronment. \\nRegister\n\nFrom The Seattle Parks Foundation
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/mucc-work-party-march-8th/
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
